- wire/template
  - support for nested expressions
    bind:format:value
  - support for expressions inside attrs
    <div class="${expr:value}">...</div>
  - restricted envEval
    - only subset of javascript
    - can be used for tracking dependencies for data-binding

- wire/track
  - transactional mutation tracking

- common
  - Static analysis of source code
    - google closure compiler
    - jslint, jshint
